<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٦١٣٢ - • وأحمد بن محمد الحنفي.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">ابن مقبل:</span> خليل <span class="c2">(٧)</span>، شارح <span class="c1">"المصابيح"</span> <span class="c2">(٨)</span>.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
